MEMORABLE.Definition: likely to be remembered or worth remembering

ANYWAY.Definition: in conversation, anyway is also used to change the subject, return to an earlier subject, or get to the most interesting point

INVEST.Definition: to put money or effort into something to make a profit or achieve a result

INVOLVE.Definition: if an activity, situation, etc. involves something, that thing is a part of the activity, etc.

INTENTIONS.Definition: something that you want and plan to do

GENEROUSLY.Definition: in a way that shows a willingness to give money, help, kindness, etc., especially more than is usual or expected

SELF-PRESERVATION.Definition: the ability of animals or people to protect themselves from danger or destruction

BRUH.Definition: used as a friendly way of addressing a man or boy

LOOKING OUT FOR.Definition: to take care or concern oneself

SPARE.Definition: if something is spare, it is available to use because it is extra

CHANGE.Definition: money in the form of coins rather than bills

RECIPROCATED.Definition: to share the same feelings as someone else, or to behave in the same way as someone else

NFT.Definition: abbreviation for non-fungible token: a unique unit of data (= the only one existing of its type) that links to a particular piece of digital art, music, video, etc. and that can be bought and sold

RISKS.Definition: the possibility of something bad happening

MINDSET.Definition: a person's way of thinking and their opinions

THRESHOLD.Definition: the level or point at which you start to experience something, or at which something starts to happen

TOLERANCE.Definition: the ability to deal with something unpleasant or annoying, or to continue existing despite bad or difficult conditions

PESSIMISTIC.Definition: thinking that bad things are more likely to happen or emphasizing the bad part of a situation

REALISTIC.Definition: accepting things as they are in fact and not making decisions based on unlikely hopes for the future

DRAW THE LINE.Definition: to put a limit on what you will do or allow to happen, esp. because you feel something is wrong

FREESTYLING.Definition: to talk without having planned what you are going to say
